TOMCAT application install and configure on Macbook
1. download tomcat from tomcat website.
2. unzip and place tomcat in any folder application/tools.
3. open terminal -> goto tomcat/bin directory and make all scripts executable; chmod +x *.sh
4. start tomcat ./startup.sh
5. shutdown to ./shutdown
-------------------------
install tomcat controller
1. download
2. unzip and run .dmg
3. configure tomcat folder in tomcat controller
4. to change default port edit /Applications/tools/apache-tomcat-8.5.14/conf/server.xml and change 8080 to 8082.
